### Get all positions
GET  http://localhost:5000/positions

### Create position
POST  http://localhost:5000/positions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "position_name" : "Production Operator",
    "base_salary" : 2000,
    "transport_allowance" : 1000,
    "meal_allowance" : 500
}

### Update position
PATCH   http://localhost:5000/positions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "position_name" : "Department Head",
    "base_salary" : 5000,
    "transport_allowance" : 2000,
    "meal_allowance" : 1000
}

### Delete position
DELETE    http://localhost:5000/positions/2